
Rime - Release Notes

Rime.py 0.3b - 2011-06-18
==========================================
  - Revised schemas.
  - Improve syllablizing experience for incomplete input.
  - Fixed an issue on moving cursor over a single phrase.

Rime.py 0.3 - 2011-06-15
==========================================
  - Improved user interaction.
    - now our auto-prompt mode mimics sogou, ziguang, pyjj and alike;
    - while sentence mode is something similar to mspy and chewing.
  - Updated pre-packaged schemas, with better abbreviation support.
  - Refactored part of the code for future maintenance.
  - Coming with two distros, ibus-rime 0.3 and Weasel 0.3.

la renaissance de la rime 0.0 - 2011-02-12
==========================================
  - new name adopted: RIME - Rime Input Method Engine
  - planning some serious work
  - introducing the idea of product management

experimental versions before `la renaissance de la rime`:

ibus-zime 3.6 - 2010-10-17
==========================
  - new zimedb-admin tool with schema install/uninstall and userdata dump/restore functionalities.
  - improve performance in schema installation process.
  - enhanced conversion algorithm with perfomance improvement and bug-fixes.
  - Tab key toggles the cursor between the beginning and then end of undetermined input.
  - backquote (`) turns existing input into raw-mode, enabling easy input for URLs and email addresses.
  - floating-point numbers like 3.14 is now traited correctly.
  - introducing schema Quick.

ibus-zime 3.5 - 2010-09-05
==========================
  - merged branch from weasel/engine.
  - updated schema files, introducing Wu - Shanghainese input.
  - add make targets for schema installation.

ibus-zime 3.4 - 2010-04-25
==========================
  - the most previously inputted pinyin is made always visible.
  - the number of candidates per page can now be defined by setting Option/PageSize (defaults to 7).
  - cancel phrase creation by hitting BackSpace within 5 seconds immediately after committing.
  - replaced Pinyin data with a Simplified Chinese dictionary from Android PinyinIME.
  - removed Zhuyin, TonalPinyin from the install package. they are still available at ZIME website.

ibus-zime 3.3.1 - 2010-03-16
============================
  - bug-fix in Makefile: create a separate libexec dir /usr/lib/ibus-zime.

ibus-zime 3.3 - 2010-02-06
==========================
  - performance enhancement.
  - improvement in candidate generation algorithm for long sentences.
  - memorize partially confirmed sentence against further editing.
  - insert delimiters to raw input committed by hitting Return.
  - bug fix: inconsistent keyword mapping in spelling algebra.

ibus-zime 3.2 - 2010-01-15
==========================
  - removed extra schemas.

ibus-zime 3.1 - 2010-01-14
==========================
  - fixed issue 2: improve backsapce key behavior in table parser.

ibus-zime 3.0 - 2010-01-13
==========================
  - adopted new schema file format as defined in ZIME Schema Specification v3.
  - full support for Spelling Algebra now implemented, enabling dict sharing between related schemas.
  - added table parser, supporting new schemas DoublePinyin, Cangjie5 and Quick.

